* [Zappa](https://github.com/Miserlou/Zappa)
* [chalice](https://github.com/aws/chalice)

## Testing
To run the test suite, first, create and activate a virtual environment. Then run tests.
```
$ flit install -s
$ cd tests
$ ./runtests.py
```

